{"tid":2071463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中美角力】被指在華為事件上勾結美國　滙豐急澄清：繼續為中國經濟做出自己貢獻","createTime":"2020-06-20T00:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T07:41:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1fbf172e0cb430bef3e02fed84bae558ad0abb4c","tid":2071463,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:10:36.000Z","msg":"【中美角力】被指在華為事件上勾結美國　滙豐急澄清：繼續為中國經濟做出自己貢獻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2674964/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%80%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%80%A5%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%9A%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%B2%A2%E7%8D%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2674964%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258B%25BE%25E7%25B5%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25BE%2584%25E6%25B8%2585%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E5%2581%259A%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%2587%25AA%25E5%25B7%25B1%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E7%258D%25BB&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=a4ac774b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2674964/%E3%80%90%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8A%E5%8B%BE%E7%B5%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%80%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%80%A5%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85%EF%BC%9A%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E5%81%9A%E5%87%BA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%B2%A2%E7%8D%BB</a><br />\n<br />\n內地官方媒體《環球時報》英文版，在周三（17日）報道中，提及該行在華為孟晚舟案中「與美國政府勾結」。今日<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滙豐中國透過微信號急澄清，指注意到網絡上出現有關滙豐的一些具有誤導性的傳言，缺乏事實依據。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n滙豐指中國是滙豐集團重要的戰略性市場。150多年來，植根中國，從未間斷為內地服務。改革開放40多年來，滙豐更是中國經濟和社會發展的堅定支持者和積極參與者。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐亦指在未來將繼續在業務、服務、人才和技術等各方面增加對內地市場的投入，一如既往地為中國經濟的可持續發展做出自己的貢獻。"},{"pid":"e7fdaf519a2517c9a0d26e090deaeceb53f7095b","tid":2071463,"uid":133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:14:08.000Z","msg":"Shanghai Bank"},{"pid":"46cdc9b04c5cf56e227e503ed0faf09d5813ca0d","tid":2071463,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:17:52.000Z","msg":"HSBC唔記得1950年，上海發生左d咩？"},{"pid":"12e366946b997d3d3caf4582731cb2351868f27d","tid":2071463,"uid":8410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:18:37.000Z","msg":"好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c626e396a771f9e1ba6e46a4c650a469427b95be","tid":2071463,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:19:00.000Z","msg":"借個位 立會事實處 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2070889/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2070889/page/1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2b4f685045de9bdf2b6d0046174ee6b4b91831","tid":2071463,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:19:13.000Z","msg":"係咪即係話我地偉大黨媒出fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209d7ffa07b50e3a970a3db822bae59f0f80e412","tid":2071463,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46cdc9b04c5cf56e227e503ed0faf09d5813ca0d","tid":2071463,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:17:52.000Z","msg":"HSBC唔記得19